I called the glass replacement company my insurance company reccomended 
and they came out and put in a windshield....  no questions asked, 
although they brought the rubber for a vanagon and had to reuse the old 
rubber but it doesn't leak.

funny thing they sent out a young guy he spent hours sweating with the 
