and can't get it in..... finally call an older guy, supervisor and he 
comes out with his truck, zips it in about 10 minutes, says these kids 
just don't know how to string a piece of glass in....,. haven't done it 
enough.

billed my insurance company about 150 dollars.\

so call your insurance company and ask em who they reccomend.

